strings:
<voice_0x01000E9D><se_low>King Clavius: Ah, perfect timing, <hero>!
Allow me to introduce my son.

<voice_0x01000E9E><se_low>King Clavius: This is Prince Charmles,
the future King of Argonia!
<voice_0x01000E9F><se_def>Prince Charmles: What is all this, Father!?
<voice_0x01000EA0><se_def>Prince Charmles: Why are you wasting my time with this riff-raff?
<voice_0x01000EA1><se_low>King Clavius: They are going to protect you during the initiation. They will need to know who you are.
<voice_0x01000EA2><se_def>Prince Charmles: Initiation!? Who said anything about the initiation? I don't recall agreeing to that!

<voice_0x01000EA3><se_def>Prince Charmles: I hate lizards!
How many times do I have to tell you!?
<voice_0x01000EA4><se_low>King Clavius: Listen carefully, Charmles.
<voice_0x01000EA5><se_low>King Clavius: Enough is enough. I am aware of your aversion to the initiation, but it remains your duty to complete it.
<voice_0x01000EA6><se_low>King Clavius: You won't be able to marry Princess Medea until you prove your worth!
<voice_0x01000EA7><se_def>Prince Charmles: Well, I don't care about getting married anyway.

<voice_0x01000EA8><se_low>King Clavius: You're making a mistake, Charmles.
I hear Princess Medea is, well...
<voice_0x01000EA9><se_low>King Clavius: Va!
<voice_0x01000EAA><se_low>King Clavius: Va!
<voice_0x01000EAB><se_low>King Clavius: VOOOM!
<voice_0x01000EAC><se_low>King Clavius: You understand what I'm saying?
<voice_0x01000EAD><se_def>Prince Charmles: Wow...
<voice_0x01000EAE><se_low>King Clavius: Now have you reconsidered?
<voice_0x01000EAF><se_high>Jessica: You can leave me out of this, thank you!
<voice_0x01000EB0><se_low>King Clavius: Ahem. Anyway, my son. Do you realise what people say about you behind your back?

<voice_0x01000EB1><se_low>King Clavius: This is your chance to prove yourself!
To show the world you are a man.

<voice_0x01000EB2><se_low>King Clavius: These people can assure your safety.
Well, Charmles, do you accept?

<voice_0x01000EB3><se_def>Prince Charmles: Uh... Yes? Wait! No! I mean...
Oh, I don't know!
<voice_0x01000EB4><se_low>King Clavius: I heard a ‘yes’! That's my Prince! I'll ensure that everyone believes you're doing it on your own.
<voice_0x01000EB5><se_low>King Clavius: You will leave now, hide yourself in the wagon at the city gates, and await your bodyguards.
<voice_0x01000EB6><se_def>Prince Charmles: R-Right now?
<voice_0x01000EB7><se_low>King Clavius: Chancellor! Accompany Charmles to the gate. The Prince is leaving for his initiation!

<voice_0x01000EB8><se_low>King Clavius: Summon the royal guards! The Prince must
have a fittingly ostentatious send-off!
Remember, he is leaving on his own!
<voice_0x01000EB9><se_low>*: It shall be as you wish, Your Majesty.
<voice_0x01000EBA><se_def>Prince Charmles: But! Wait! I'm not ready yet...
<voice_0x01000EBB><se_low>King Clavius: Off at last. I wish you luck. And remember, <hero>: your mission is top secret.
<voice_0x01000EBC><se_low>King Clavius: Charmles will explain the details of the initiation himself.
<voice_0x01000EBD><se_low>King Clavius: Fulfil my request, and you have my word that the magic mirror shall be yours.
